{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01CvKk4FLs98xwZTJaB4rzBC","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/validator/ModelValidator.java has been updated. Here's the result of running `cat -n` on a snippet of the edited file:\n     1→package org.example.realworldapi.domain.validator;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.validation.ConstraintViolation;\n     4→import jakarta.validation.Validator;\n     5→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.exception.ModelValidationException;\n     6→import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\n     7→import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n     8→\n     9→import java.util.Set;\n    10→import java.util.stream.Collectors;\n    11→\n    12→@Component\n    13→public class ModelValidator {\n    14→\n    15→    @Autowired\n    16→    private Validator validator;\n    17→\n    18→    public <T> T validate(T model) {\n    19→        Set<ConstraintViolation<T>> constraintViolations = validator.validate(model);\n    20→\n    21→        if (!constraintViolations.isEmpty()) {\n    22→            final var messages =\n    23→                    constraintViolations.stream()\n    24→                            .map(ConstraintViolation::getMessage)\n    25→                            .collect(Collectors.toList());\n    26→            throw new ModelValidationException(messages);\n    27→        }\n    28→\n    29→        return model;\n    30→    }\n    31→}\n    32→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01MEcXaqNzvgkgxmWL4aKDiD","session_id":"df1561a9-af26-4e6c-a6ca-e235ecd783f5","uuid":"6085be96-4d15-4b92-b0a3-66fa594cea63"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01MhF18yNWr612aMRb1m4H5j","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated all 6 REST controller/resource files from JAX-RS to Spring Boot. Let me create a summary of the changes:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully rewritten all REST controller/resource files from Jakarta EE JAX-RS to Spring Boot Spring MVC. Here's what was changed:\n\n### Files Migrated:\n\n1. **ArticlesResource.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java)\n2. **ProfilesResource.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java)\n3. **TagsResource.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/TagsResource.java)\n4. **UserResource.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java)\n5. **UsersResource.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java)\n6. **ResourceUtils.java** (/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java)\n\n### Key Migration Changes Applied:\n\n**Annotations:**\n- `@Path(\"/path\")` → `@RequestMapping(\"/api/path\")` (added /api prefix)\n- `@GET` → `@GetMapping`\n- `@POST` → `@PostMapping`\n- `@PUT` → `@PutMapping`\n- `@DELETE` → `@DeleteMapping`\n- `@PathParam` → `@PathVariable`\n- `@QueryParam` → `@RequestParam`\n- `@Context SecurityContext` → `@RequestAttribute UUID loggedUserId`\n- `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n- `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Service` (in ResourceUtils)\n- Added `@RestController` to all controller classes\n- `@Transactional` changed from `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` to `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n\n**Response Handling:**\n- `jakarta.ws.rs.core.Response` → `org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity`\n- `Response.ok().build()` → `ResponseEntity.ok().build()`\n- `Response.ok(body).status(Status.CREATED)` → `ResponseEntity.status(HttpStatus.CREATED).body(body)`\n- Removed manual JSON serialization with ObjectMapper - Spring now handles serialization automatically\n- Removed `JsonProcessingException` from method signatures\n\n**Import Changes:**\n- Removed all `jakarta.ws.rs.*` imports\n- Added Spring Web imports: `org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.*`\n- Added Spring HTTP imports: `org.springframework.http.*`\n- Added Spring transaction imports: `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n\n**Security Context:**\n- Removed `@Secured` annotations (security will be handled by JWT filter)\n- Replaced `SecurityContext` parameter with `@RequestAttribute UUID loggedUserId`\n- Used `required = false` for optional authentication\n- Removed `getLoggedUserId()` method from ResourceUtils (no longer needed)\n\n**Other Changes:**\n- Removed ObjectMapper injections (Spring handles JSON serialization)\n- Removed `@NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper` qualifier usage\n- Kept `@Valid` for request body validation using jakarta.validation.Valid\n- Default values on @RequestParam for offset/limit parameters\n\nAll endpoints maintain the same functionality and business logic, only the web framework annotations and response handling have been changed from JAX-RS to Spring MVC."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"df1561a9-af26-4e6c-a6ca-e235ecd783f5","uuid":"82a1a8a0-08ec-4e40-b119-df51e156d46b"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01UEpsvtrVP76dBbJYFcqiHR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01YZtnFwQkeRmcWLqjXSfgUw","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/entity/EntityUtils.java","content":"package org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.repository.entity;\n\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.Article;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.ArticleModelBuilder;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.FavoriteRelationship;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.article.TagRelationship;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.comment.Comment;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.comment.CommentBuilder;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.tag.Tag;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.tag.TagBuilder;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.user.User;\nimport org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.user.UserModelBuilder;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;\nimport org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Component;\n\n@Component\npublic class EntityUtils {\n\n    @Autowired\n    @Qualifier(\"usermodelbuilder\")\n    private UserModelBuilder userBuilder;\n    @Autowired\n    private TagBuilder tagBuilder;\n    @Autowired\n    private ArticleModelBuilder articleBuilder;\n    @Autowired\n    private CommentBuilder commentBuilder;\n\n    public User user(UserEntity userEntity) {\n        final var id = userEntity.getId();\n        final var username = userEntity.getUsername();\n        final var bio = userEntity.getBio();\n        final var image = userEntity.getImage();\n        final var password = userEntity.getPassword();\n        final var email = userEntity.getEmail();\n        return userBuilder.build(id, username, bio, image, password, email);\n    }\n\n    public Tag tag(TagEntity tagEntity) {\n        return tagBuilder.build(tagEntity.getId(), tagEntity.getName());\n    }\n\n    public Tag tag(TagRelationshipEntity tagRelationshipEntity) {\n        return tag(tagRelationshipEntity.getTag());\n    }\n\n    public TagRelationship tagRelationship(TagRelationshipEntity tagRelationshipEntity) {\n        return new TagRelationship(article(tagRelationshipEntity.getArticle()), tag(tagRelationshipEntity.getTag()));\n    }\n\n    public Article article(ArticleEntity articleEntity) {\n        return articleBuilder.build(\n                articleEntity.getId(),\n                articleEntity.getSlug(),\n                articleEntity.getTitle(),\n                articleEntity.getDescription(),\n                articleEntity.getBody(),\n                articleEntity.getCreatedAt(),\n                articleEntity.getUpdatedAt(),\n                user(articleEntity.getAuthor()));\n    }\n\n    public Comment comment(CommentEntity commentEntity) {\n        return commentBuilder.build(\n                commentEntity.getId(),\n                user(commentEntity.getAuthor()),\n                article(commentEntity.getArticle()),\n                commentEntity.getBody(),\n                commentEntity.getCreatedAt(),\n                commentEntity.getUpdatedAt());\n    }\n\n    public FavoriteRelationship favoriteRelationship(\n            FavoriteRelationshipEntity favoriteRelationshipEntity) {\n        return new FavoriteRelationship(\n                user(favoriteRelationshipEntity.getUser()),\n                article(favoriteRelationshipEntity.getArticle()));\n    }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2626,"cache_read_input_tokens":43788,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2626,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":979},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01BDn9jiVzETnWraGJQhAeLr","session_id":"df1561a9-af26-4e6c-a6ca-e235ecd783f5","uuid":"208e460a-a17f-4eac-88c3-ee1f108948cf"}
