{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01MEcXaqNzvgkgxmWL4aKDiD","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated all domain layer files from Jakarta EE/CDI to Spring Boot. Let me create a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all domain layer files from Jakarta EE/OpenLiberty with CDI annotations to Spring Boot. Here's what was changed:\n\n### **Model Builders and Validators (5 files)**\n\n1. **ArticleModelBuilder.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/article/ArticleModelBuilder.java`\n   - Changed `@Singleton` → `@Component`\n   - Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n   - Updated imports\n\n2. **UserModelBuilder.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/user/UserModelBuilder.java`\n   - Changed `@Singleton` → `@Component(\"usermodelbuilder\")`\n   - Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n   - Preserved the named component qualifier\n   - Updated imports\n\n3. **CommentBuilder.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/comment/CommentBuilder.java`\n   - Changed `@Singleton` → `@Component`\n   - Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n   - Updated imports\n\n4. **TagBuilder.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/tag/TagBuilder.java`\n   - Changed `@Singleton` → `@Component`\n   - Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n   - Updated imports\n\n5. **ModelValidator.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/validator/ModelValidator.java`\n   - Changed `@Singleton` → `@Component`\n   - Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n   - Updated imports\n   - Kept jakarta.validation imports (as required)\n\n### **Feature Implementations (29 files)**\n\nAll 29 feature implementation files in `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/`:\n\n- ArticleFavoritesCountImpl.java\n- CreateArticleImpl.java\n- CreateCommentImpl.java\n- CreateSlugByTitleImpl.java\n- CreateTagImpl.java\n- CreateUserImpl.java\n- DeleteArticleBySlugImpl.java\n- DeleteCommentImpl.java\n- FavoriteArticleImpl.java\n- FindArticleByAuthorAndSlugImpl.java\n- FindArticleByIdImpl.java\n- FindArticleBySlugImpl.java\n- FindArticleTagsImpl.java\n- FindArticlesByFilterImpl.java\n- FindCommentByIdAndAuthorImpl.java\n- FindCommentsByArticleSlugImpl.java\n- FindMostRecentArticlesByFilterImpl.java\n- FindTagsByNameCreateIfNotExistsImpl.java\n- FindTagsImpl.java\n- FindUserByIdImpl.java\n- FindUserByUsernameImpl.java\n- FollowUserByUsernameImpl.java\n- IsArticleFavoritedImpl.java\n- IsFollowingUserImpl.java\n- LoginUserImpl.java\n- UnfavoriteArticleImpl.java\n- UnfollowUserByUsernameImpl.java\n- UpdateArticleBySlugImpl.java\n- UpdateUserImpl.java\n\n**Changes applied to each:**\n- Changed `@Singleton` or `@Dependent` → `@Component`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n- Removed `jakarta.inject.Inject`, `jakarta.inject.Singleton`, and `jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent` imports\n- Added `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired` and `org.springframework.stereotype.Component` imports\n- All business logic preserved unchanged\n\n### **Request Model Files (3 files)**\n\nRemoved `jakarta.json.bind.annotation.JsonbNillable` import from:\n\n1. **NewArticleRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/NewArticleRequest.java`\n2. **NewCommentRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/NewCommentRequest.java`\n3. **UpdateArticleRequest.java** - `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/UpdateArticleRequest.java`\n\n### **Migration Rules Applied**\n\n- `@Singleton` → `@Component`\n- `@Dependent` → `@Component`\n- `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n- `jakarta.inject.Named` → `@Component(\"name\")` (preserved naming)\n- Removed `jakarta.inject.*` imports\n- Removed `jakarta.enterprise.context.*` imports\n- Added Spring imports: `org.springframework.stereotype.Component` and `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n- Kept `jakarta.validation.*` annotations unchanged (they work in Spring Boot)\n- Kept `jakarta.persistence.*` annotations unchanged\n- Removed `jakarta.json.bind.*` imports from request models\n\n**Total: 37 files migrated successfully**\n\nAll domain layer files have been successfully migrated from Jakarta EE CDI to Spring Boot dependency injection, maintaining all business logic while updating only the dependency injection framework annotations."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"df1561a9-af26-4e6c-a6ca-e235ecd783f5","uuid":"c7283be8-a0e7-47aa-be25-c44ad9b95025"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01BDn9jiVzETnWraGJQhAeLr","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good, it's not being used anywhere else. Now let me create a summary document listing all the migrated files:\n\n## Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated ALL infrastructure layer files from Jakarta EE/OpenLiberty to Spring Boot. Here's a comprehensive summary of the changes made:\n\n### Configuration Files\n\n**1. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/config/SerializerConfig.java**\n- Changed `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Configuration`\n- Changed `@Produces` → `@Bean`\n- Changed `@Singleton` → removed (not needed with `@Bean`)\n- Added `@Primary` annotation to the main ObjectMapper bean\n- Used `@Bean(\"noWrapObjectMapper\")` to name the secondary ObjectMapper\n\n**2. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/config/WebConfig.java** (NEW)\n- Created new Spring MVC configuration class\n- Registered `AuthenticationFilter` as an interceptor for `/api/**` paths\n- Added CORS configuration\n\n### Provider Classes\n\n**3. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/BCryptHashProvider.java**\n- Changed `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n\n**4. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/JwtTokenProvider.java**\n- Changed `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n- Changed `@Inject` → removed (using constructor injection)\n- Changed `@ConfigProperty(name=\"x\")` → `@Value(\"${x}\")`\n- Fixed cast issue in `plusMinutes` method\n\n**5. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/SlugifySlugProvider.java**\n- Changed `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n- Removed `@Inject` from constructor (not needed in Spring)\n\n### Web Security & Filters\n\n**6. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/security/filter/AuthenticationFilter.java**\n- Converted from JAX-RS `ContainerRequestFilter` to Spring `HandlerInterceptor`\n- Changed `@Provider` and `@Priority` → `@Component`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n- Converted from JAX-RS `ContainerRequestContext` to servlet `HttpServletRequest` and `HttpServletResponse`\n- Removed security context setting logic (handled differently in Spring)\n- Stores JWT information as request attributes\n\n### Exception Handling\n\n**7. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/web/mapper/BeanValidationExceptionMapper.java**\n- Converted from JAX-RS `ExceptionMapper` to Spring `@RestControllerAdvice`\n- Changed `@Provider` → `@RestControllerAdvice`\n- Removed `@Inject` for ObjectMapper (handled by Spring directly via `@ExceptionHandler` return types)\n- Converted JAX-RS `Response` to Spring `ResponseEntity<ErrorResponse>`\n- Added handlers for all domain exceptions:\n  - `ConstraintViolationException`\n  - `MethodArgumentNotValidException` (Spring's validation exception)\n  - `EmailAlreadyExistsException`\n  - `UsernameAlreadyExistsException`\n  - `UserNotFoundException`\n  - `ArticleNotFoundException`\n  - `CommentNotFoundException`\n  - `TagNotFoundException`\n  - `InvalidPasswordException`\n  - `ModelValidationException`\n  - `UnauthorizedException`\n  - `ForbiddenException`\n- Renamed class to `GlobalExceptionHandler` to better reflect its purpose\n\n### Repository Entity Utilities\n\n**8. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/entity/EntityUtils.java**\n- Changed `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Component`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n- Changed `@Named(\"usermodelbuilder\")` → `@Qualifier(\"usermodelbuilder\")`\n\n### Data Access Objects (DAOs)\n\n**9. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/AbstractDAO.java**\n- No changes needed (already using standard JPA annotations)\n\n**10. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/ArticleDAO.java**\n- Changed `@ApplicationScoped` → `@Repository`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n**11. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/UserDAO.java**\n- Changed `@Singleton` → `@Repository`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n**12. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/CommentDAO.java**\n- Changed `@Dependent` → `@Repository`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n**13. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/TagDAO.java**\n- Changed `@Dependent` → `@Repository`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n**14. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/FavoriteRelationshipDAO.java**\n- Changed `@Dependent` → `@Repository`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n**15. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/FollowRelationshipDAO.java**\n- Changed `@Dependent` → `@Repository`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n**16. /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/TagRelationshipDAO.java**\n- Changed `@Dependent` → `@Repository`\n- Changed `@Inject` → `@Autowired`\n\n### Key Migration Patterns Applied\n\n1. **Dependency Injection**:\n   - `@ApplicationScoped` / `@Singleton` / `@Dependent` → `@Component` / `@Service` / `@Repository` / `@Configuration`\n   - `@Inject` → `@Autowired` (or constructor injection)\n   - `@Named(\"x\")` → `@Qualifier(\"x\")`\n\n2. **Configuration**:\n   - `@Produces` → `@Bean`\n   - MicroProfile `@ConfigProperty(name=\"x\")` → Spring `@Value(\"${x}\")`\n\n3. **Web Layer**:\n   - JAX-RS `@Provider` → Spring `@Component` or `@RestControllerAdvice`\n   - JAX-RS `ContainerRequestFilter` → Spring `HandlerInterceptor`\n   - JAX-RS `ExceptionMapper` → Spring `@ExceptionHandler` in `@RestControllerAdvice`\n   - JAX-RS `Response` → Spring `ResponseEntity`\n\n4. **Persistence**:\n   - `@PersistenceContext EntityManager` remains the same (standard JPA)\n   - All repository implementations changed to use `@Repository`\n\nAll infrastructure layer files have been successfully migrated to Spring Boot while maintaining the same functionality and architecture. The JPA persistence layer remains unchanged as it uses standard JPA annotations that work with both Jakarta EE and Spring."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"df1561a9-af26-4e6c-a6ca-e235ecd783f5","uuid":"80b78bc5-9526-46f5-991c-3f608bbfe75d"}
