{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WmQvJZzjN6syFdYH1J59Vc","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'll now summarize the files I found:\n\nRequest Models (in src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/request/):\n1. NewArticleRequestWrapper.java - Wrapper for creating a new article\n2. LoginRequest.java - Handles login credentials\n3. LoginRequestWrapper.java - Wrapper for login request\n4. UpdateUserRequestWrapper.java - Wrapper for updating user details\n5. UpdateArticleRequestWrapper.java - Wrapper for updating an article\n6. UpdateUserRequest.java - Contains fields for updating user profile\n7. NewUserRequestWrapper.java - Wrapper for creating a new user\n8. NewUserRequest.java - Contains fields for creating a new user\n9. NewCommentRequestWrapper.java - Wrapper for creating a new comment\n10. NewArticleRequest.java - Contains fields for creating a new article\n11. NewCommentRequest.java - Contains fields for creating a new comment\n12. UpdateArticleRequest.java - Contains fields for updating an article\n\nResponse Models (in src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/model/response/):\n1. ProfileResponse.java - Represents a user's profile\n2. ErrorResponse.java - Handles error responses\n3. CommentResponse.java - Represents a comment\n4. TagsResponse.java - Handles list of tags\n5. ArticleResponse.java - Represents an article\n6. CommentsResponse.java - Contains a list of comments\n7. ArticlesResponse.java - Contains a list of articles\n8. UserResponse.java - Represents a user's details\n\nWould you like me to elaborate on any of these files or their contents?"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"df1561a9-af26-4e6c-a6ca-e235ecd783f5","uuid":"224163c1-03f6-4d8b-8b5f-39d96f982894"}
